code: @Test public void convertShouldConvertIsoDate() {     IsoOffsetDateTimeConverter converter = new IsoOffsetDateTimeConverter().     OffsetDateTime time = converter.convert("2011-12-03T10:15:30+01:00").     assertThat(time).isNotNull(). }

@Test public void registerConverterShouldRegister() {     DefaultConversionService service = new DefaultConversionService().     IsoOffsetDateTimeConverter.registerConverter(service).     OffsetDateTime time = service.convert("2011-12-03T10:15:30+01:00", OffsetDateTime.class).     assertThat(time).isNotNull(). }
